Package: SeuratBasics
Version: 0.0.99
Date: 2020-04-12
Title: Slimmed down version of Seurat
Description: 
    Seurat is an awesome package for scRNA-seq data analysis, but its numerous
    dependencies means that it takes a long time to install Seurat on Linux
    systems. This is a slimmed down version of Seurat, only keeping the most
    commonly used features, to reduce the number of dependencies. This is very
    helpful for Google Colab tutorials using Seurat and for web services that
    involve Seurat but are impeded by the numerous dependencies.
